00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:34.960
Tolong katakan ya.

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.960
Bagus.

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:43.160
Terima kasih.

00:03:44.800 --> 00:03:45.760
Saya harus pergi.

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:49.000
Jangan khawatir.

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.160
Apapun yang terjadi,

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.640
Aku akan membawa Rani kembali.

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:07.240
Anda tidak akan pergi sendirian.

00:04:08.440 --> 00:04:10.480
Iya gan.  Aku akan pergi bersamamu.

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:11.400
TIDAK.

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:12.760
Tapi, kawan...
- Vikram.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:15.400
