00:04:40.520 --> 00:04:42.080
Saya harus melawan pertempuran ini sendirian.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:46.520
Membelok!

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.720
Tolong jaga dirimu baik-baik.

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:14.240
Paman, ikutlah denganku.

00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:24.680
saya senang

00:05:27.040 --> 00:05:30.120
