00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:19.880
'Aku mendatangimu, Rani.'

00:06:20.280 --> 00:06:23.800
'Kamu mengalami begitu
banyak rasa sakit dan siksaan.'

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:26.080
'Aku akan
membebaskanmu darinya.'

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:28.000
'Jangan kehilangan harapan.'

